name: Better Skin Fang - Concept
description:
This LORA will help you generate a skin fang on your characters more consistently.

Use with a weight between 0.6-0.8

Use Hi-Res fix for cowboy/full body shots. Might need to play with the weights a bit to especially for wide shots.

Works with closed mouths too!

Have fun!

modelVersions.name: skin fang
modelVersions.description: The base version, use with a weight of 0.6-0.8
